OL,4,Csongwriting helped me grieve for my
OL,5,Cfather
OL,7,FWATCH: ITV News Meridian's Rachel
OL,8,FHepworth spoke to Josie at her home in
OL,9,FTurner's Hill, West Sussex.
OL,11,FIt's been five years since Josie Quin
OL,12,Flost her father, but not a day passes
OL,13,Fthat she doesn't think of him.
OL,15,F"He was such a charismatic man," she
OL,16,Fsaid. "He was just the heartbeat of
OL,17,Four family.
OL,19,F"He had so many passions and hobbies.
OL,20,FHe loved motorbikes, boating, music.
