OL,5,Cfather
OL,7,FAndrew and Josie appeared together on
OL,8,FITV News Meridian in 2000, when he was
OL,9,Ffighting for hepatitis treatment
OL,10,Fbecause of a postcode lottery.
OL,12,FUnbelievably, and rather tellingly,
OL,13,Finfected blood didn't even figure as
OL,14,Fpart of the story.
OL,16,F"How crazy is that?" said Josie, "That
OL,17,Fwe didn't even mention it in the
OL,18,Finterview? That my dad had been
OL,19,Finfected by medical negligence.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
