OL,7,FLike thousands of others, poor health
OL,8,Fmeant he had to give up work, as did
OL,9,Fhis wife, to care for him. He was
OL,10,Fostracised for having Hepatitis C, and
OL,11,Ferroneously accused of drug use and
OL,12,Fpromiscuity to explain his diagnosis.
OL,14,FHe struggled on, but was unable to
OL,15,Flive his life to the full, and liver
OL,16,Ffailure finally look him during the
OL,17,Fcovid pandemic in 2020.
OL,19,F"We weren't able to have a proper
OL,20,Ffuneral for him," said Josie. "He died
OL,21,Fthe day before his 70th birthday.
