OL,3,CInfected Blood Scandal - How
OL,4,Csongwriting helped me grieve for my
OL,5,Cfather
OL,7,F"Dad was from Scotland and we'd
OL,8,Farranged to get a bagpipe player to
OL,9,Fstand outside the house and play for
OL,10,Fhim.
OL,12,F"We didn't want to cancel, so he
OL,13,Fplayed in dad's honour instead. All
OL,14,Fthe neighbours came out to watch too,
OL,15,Fit was very emotional."
OL,17,FAlongside the personal loss, she's
OL,18,Fangry that justice, and an apology
OL,19,Fcame too late.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
