OL,3,CInfected Blood Scandal - How
OL,4,Csongwriting helped me grieve for my
OL,5,Cfather
OL,7,FThough grateful to the public inquiry,
OL,8,Fshe believes action should have been
OL,9,Ftaken much sooner.
OL,11,F"Everyone has been waiting long
OL,12,Fenough. And, you know, it's decades.
OL,13,FPeople have been waiting not just for
OL,14,Fthe inquiry, but obviously for the
OL,15,Foutcome and the compensation, so I
OL,16,Fwould just hope that there's no more
OL,17,Fdragging of heels before too many more
OL,18,Fpeople pass away."
