OL,3,CInfected Blood Scandal - How
OL,4,Csongwriting helped me grieve for my
OL,5,Cfather
OL,7,FMusic is a huge part of Josie's life.
OL,8,FA talented session singer, she's found
OL,9,Fthat writing music has helped her to
OL,10,Fprocess her grief and create something
OL,11,Fpositive.
OL,13,FNow she's released the song "Faces",
OL,14,Finspired by the hundreds of people who
OL,15,Ftold their stories at the Infected
OL,16,FBlood Inquiry.
OL,18,F"I really struggled with my grief and
OL,19,Fhow to express my emotion," she said.
