OL,3,CInfected Blood Scandal - How
OL,4,Csongwriting helped me grieve for my
OL,5,Cfather
OL,7,F"After my dad passed away it really
OL,8,Fhelped. It was a great healing process
OL,9,Ffor me to write that song. And it
OL,10,Fhelped me express and channel my
OL,11,Femotion. So I wrote that song not only
OL,12,Fas a tribute to all those that passed
OL,13,Faway, but as part of my healing
OL,14,Fprocess.
OL,16,F"My wish is that it will be part of
OL,17,Fother people's healing process as
OL,18,Fwell."
