OL,7,FThe song has been embraced and backed
OL,8,Fby the blood community, and will raise
OL,9,Fmoney for the Sussex charity Taylor-
OL,10,FMade Dreams, which helps children with
OL,11,Flife-limiting conditions fulfil their
OL,12,Fambitions.
OL,14,FJosie hopes the song will create
OL,15,Fsomething positive - and serve as a
OL,16,Freminder that the Infected Blood
OL,17,Fscandal is still far from over.
